('Sittipong Wongsomboon', 'Sittipong', 'Wongsomboon', 'Co-founder @ Eiiga | Managing Director at Northern Smile Travel (DMC) | Founder, Touring Center | MICE • Tailor-Made Travel • Experience Design | Thailand & Indochina | 20+ Years in Travel Operations', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/sittipong-wongsomboon', 'sittipong-wongsomboon', $${"about": "I have been working in the travel and hospitality industry for over 20 years, with a focus on delivering well-structured and meaningful travel experiences across Thailand and Indochina.\n \nMy journey began in hospitality with Four Seasons Chiang Mai, followed by experience in airline reservations, before returning to the resort environment. These early roles shaped my understanding of service, detail, and guest experience.\n \nToday, as Managing Director of Northern Smile Travel and founder of Touring Center, I work across both operational and experiential aspects of travel.\n \nNorthern Smile Travel focuses on destination management, MICE, and logistics — supporting travel agents, corporate clients, and partners in delivering tailor-made programs, from small private journeys to large-scale operations.\n \nTouring Center, on the other hand, focuses on experience design — creating smaller, more immersive journeys that connect people with local culture, community, and place.\n \nOver time, these two perspectives have become closely connected.\n \nA well-designed experience requires strong execution.\n And strong execution only becomes meaningful when it supports the experience itself.\n \nThis is where I focus my work — ensuring that every element, from planning to delivery, comes together in a way that feels natural, structured, and reliable.\n \nI believe that in travel, details may not always be seen — but they are always felt.", "addressCountryOnly": "Thailand", "addressWithCountry": "Chiang Mai, Thailand", "addressWithoutCountry": "Chiang Mai", "backgroundPic": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5616AQHWsuv3kLO9TA/pr